images.description: SDSS image of region near elliptical galaxy NGC 3193, also showing NGC 3190, both of which are members of Arp 316 and Hickson Compact Group 44
SDSS image of elliptical galaxy NGC 3193, also known (with spiral galaxies NGC 3187 and 3190) as Arp 316, and also a member of Hickson Compact Group 44
